      "caption": "And when it is finally time to speak, fear can lock your mouth completely shut."
    },
    {
      "image": "van_kho_khan_trong_260716_145510/images/scene-05.jpg",
      "audio": "van_kho_khan_trong_260716_145510/audio/scene-05.mp3",
